HEADWORD: Monopsychism
<hw>Mon`o*psy"chism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Mono-</ets> + Gr. <?/ soul.]</ety> <def>The doctrine that
there is but one immortal soul or intellect with which all men are
endowed.</def>⟦br⟧
